<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CISIA Spot Alert</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sign Up for CISIA Spot Alerts</h1>
        <p>This site checks the CISIA calendar for open CENT@HOME / CENT@CASA spots every 30 seconds and sends you a Telegram message when they become available.</p>
        
        <p><strong>How to get your Telegram Chat ID:</strong><br>
        1. Open Telegram app.<br>
        2. Search for @userinfobot (or @RawDataBot).<br>
        3. Start chat â€” it replies instantly with your ID (a long number like 123456789).<br>
        4. Copy that number and paste here.</p>
        
        <form action="/signup" method="POST">
            <label for="chatId">Your Telegram Chat ID:</label>
            <input type="text" id="chatId" name="chatId" required placeholder="e.g., 123456789" pattern="\d+" title="Only numbers allowed">
            <button type="submit">Sign Up & Get Alerts</button>
        </form>
        
        <% if (message) { %>
            <p class="message"><%= message %></p>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
